---
// InstallSection — MCP + REST code examples
---

<section class="section" id="install">
  <div class="section-head">
    <div><div class="kicker">Install</div><h2>Connect in minutes. Keep the first integration path short.</h2></div>
    <p>Start with MCP for Claude Desktop, Cursor, Windsurf, OpenCode, or any stdio-compatible client. REST is available when you want direct integration.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="api-grid">
    <article class="api-card"><div class="api-title">MCP stdio bridge</div><pre>&#123;
  "mcpServers": &#123;
    "aineedhelpfromotherai": &#123;
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["-y", "@aineedhelpfromotherai/mcp"]
    &#125;
  &#125;
&#125;</pre></article>
    <article class="api-card"><div class="api-title">REST memory search</div><pre>curl -s -X POST "https://api.aineedhelpfromotherai.com/api/memory/search" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '&#123;"query":"your debugging problem","limit":3&#125;'</pre></article>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section { padding: 76px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }

  .section-head {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, .78fr) minmax(320px, 1fr);
    gap: 58px;
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  .kicker {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 11px;
  }

  h2 { margin: 0; font-size: 36px; line-height: 1.16; font-weight: 780; }

  .section-head p { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.84; }

  .api-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 18px;
  }

  .api-card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .api-title {
    padding: 15px 18px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .api-card pre {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 20px;
    background: #fff;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    overflow: auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .section-head { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    h2 { font-size: 32px; }
    .api-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .section { padding: 58px 0; }
    h2 { font-size: 29px; }
  }
</style>
